Content:
Your rephrasing is better. For example, there&#x27;s no reason to do:<p><pre><code>    typeof someVar === &#x27;number&#x27;
</code></pre>
...because `typeof` always returns a string, by spec[1]<p>1. <a href="http://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-11.4.3" rel="nofollow">http://www.ecma-international.org/ecma-262/5.1/#sec-11.4.3</a>
